  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 75-67-517, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO AUTHORIZE A CHECK CASHING BUSINESS TO PASS A THIRD-PARTY PROCESSING COMPANY'S FEES FOR THE USE OF A DEBIT OR CREDIT CARD ON TO THE CUSTOMER; TO AMEND SECTION 75-67-619, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO AUTHORIZE A LICENSEE WHO IS AUTHORIZED TO PROVIDE CREDIT AVAILABILITY TRANSACTIONS TO PASS A THIRD-PARTY PROCESSING COMPANY'S FEES FOR THE USE OF A DEBIT OR CREDIT CARD ON TO THE CUSTOMER; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
